values.comment:
Create a vector from a single float

   fromFloat 10 == new 10 10

   fromFloat 20 == fromRecord { x = 20, y = 20 }

Create the unit vector (1, 0)

   positiveX == fromRecord { x = 1, y = 0 }

   positiveX == new 1 0

Create the unit vector (0, 1)

   positiveY == fromRecord { x = 0, y = 1 }

   positiveY == new 0 1

